imdb.plot outline: Andy, Sandy, Nat and Shah head out to the forest edge for a night of scientific adventure. They were hanging out in the tent when suddenly, they hear a loud crash. Nat brings home a metal sphere that he found in the forest and shows it to the Sky Shakers. Meanwhile, a furry creature makes its way to Andy's house in search of the sphere that Nat found. Little did anyone know that a group of Henchmen have just landed in the forest of Singapore, in search of the furry creature.
